ğŸš€ Quick Example : 
```bash
import LittleLearn as ll 

x_train = 'your datasets'
y_train = 'your target'

model = ll.DeepLearning.Model.AutoBuildModel(type='mlp-binaryclassification',level='balance')
model.fit(x_train,y_train.reshape(-1,1),epochs=10,verbose=1)
```
